{"tid":1605353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"銅鑼灣的士疑撞記者後司機被圍 車身遭示威者大肆破壞","createTime":"2019-09-30T09:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T09:50:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"37ea207c892ec8355e9f644f9919badc21a73f06","tid":1605353,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:13:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1602055/即時-港聞-修例風波-銅鑼灣的士疑撞記者後司機被圍-車身遭示威者大肆破壞\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1602055%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E9%8A%85%E9%91%BC%E7%81%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E7%96%91%E6%92%9E%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%BE%8C%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%A2%AB%E5%9C%8D-%E8%BB%8A%E8%BA%AB%E9%81%AD%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%A4%A7%E8%82%86%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86Zvkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=71835c31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1602055%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E9%8A%85%E9%91%BC%E7%81%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E7%96%91%E6%92%9E%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%BE%8C%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%A2%AB%E5%9C%8D-%E8%BB%8A%E8%BA%AB%E9%81%AD%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%A4%A7%E8%82%86%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E&h=409fe5ca\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1602055/即時-港聞-修例風波-銅鑼灣的士疑撞記者後司機被圍-車身遭示威者大肆破壞</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190929/_2019092922054327199.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190929%2F_2019092922054327199.jpg&h=1fded0e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n的士遭示威者大肆破壞<br />\n警方入夜後在灣仔多次施放催淚彈驅散。防暴警察晚上7時在北海中心對開軒尼詩道組成防線，與數百米外示威者對峙。防暴警察晚上近8時並向西面推進。軒尼詩道多輛警車被示威者掟石及雜物，有行駛中警車司機位玻璃被擊碎。<br />\n<br />\n在軒尼詩道及菲林明道一帶，有人多次將燃燒物品投擲在馬路，亦有人帶同石油氣罐到現場。<br />\n<br />\n晚上8時，警方在鵝頸橋附近先後舉起黑旗及橙旗，現場仍有不少人聚集，並高叫「光復香港，時代革命」等口號，多名持槍警員在場戒備。晚上8時07分，警方再舉黑旗，其後再次推進，並驅散在場示威者。警方其後在灣仔一帶截查在場人士。另外，在晚上約7時許，現場消息指，有的士在堅拿道西近軒尼詩道撞倒記者後，被在場的示威者包圍。的士司機其後離開。<br />\n<br />\n至晚上約9時半，一批示威者破壞無人看守的的士，車頭擋風玻璃爆裂，示威者又打開車頭，破壞車頭的汽車零件，淋潑液體。的士兩邊車門、車窗損毀，車身被人塗鴉。示威者又阻止現場記者拍攝。其後消防到場處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190929/_2019092922054515692.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190929%2F_2019092922054515692.jpg&h=2f7f632b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190929/_2019092922054742156.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190929%2F_2019092922054742156.jpg&h=7e195264&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfa2e5ca74ca0c4e75165a6df5267ff20d2b1178","tid":1605353,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:13:56.000Z","msg":"尋晚有無巴絲 / 記者影到的士司機個證 (通常放車頭)??"},{"pid":"1e4f8f2ac308d1bed09f975fc64a2e3c43cdd70f","tid":1605353,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:14:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b88477f8b9f83f106d4c201da13d255e886e0720","tid":1605353,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:38:07.000Z","msg":"的士司機斷左手腳未？"},{"pid":"59d7326d86419586acf1639215826581d5a7d04e","tid":1605353,"uid":282347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:50:44.000Z","msg":"咁撚賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撞記者就輕輕帶過，內文就描繪到我地義士冇啦啦圍的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}